Author: livipup
Text: It would be unhealthy. Men are supposed to be at least 5% body fat and women are supposed to be at least 20%. You of course could get rid of all your fat, but it wouldn't be a good idea. At my lowest weight I was only at 12% and I was always so tired. I was also much more sick than I am now at a more healthy weight.

Author: pregonaut
Text: I do the exact same thing. I think theres always going to be a little bit of fat.
